# 14. Frequently Asked Questions

### Q1. Can I skip modules?

No. The modules are designed with dependencies. Skipping foundational topics often leads to confusion later.

### Q2. Is this course focused only on AI?

No. It combines software engineering fundamentals with AI-assisted development. Strong engineering skills remain the foundation.

### Q3. Will theory slow me down?

Initially, theory requires patience, but it accelerates practical work because you understand *why* you're making technical decisions.

